article.description: — Max Klesmit had 21 points as Wofford easily defeated Presbyterian 76-49 on Saturday.
article.headline: Klesmit scores 21 to lift Wofford over Presbyterian 76-49
article.linkText: Klesmit scores 21 to lift Wofford over Presbyterian 76-49
article.story: CLINTON, S.C. -- — Max Klesmit had 21 points as Wofford easily defeated Presbyterian 76-49 on Saturday. Isaiah Bigelow had 14 points for the Terriers (8-4). Sam Godwin added 11 points. B.J. Mack had 10 points. Rayshon Harrison had 15 points for the Blue Hose (7-6). Trevon Reddish added 13 points and six rebounds. Winston Hill had nine rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
